snippet.title: Black Mesa: Military - DARK SIDE of modding documentary 👿
snippet.description: Here is all the evidence I gathered. I was treated very badly by this person, I have proof I was, so why not show it to the world? Comment section will be opened and I won't be removing any comments so that everything will be visible, without any lies. He has a youtube channel with lots of subscribtions so I may be at a disadvantage at that, but I believe the people stand for justice and truth.
